column5: Did another boat run today with my son and the father in law. My kid of course our fished me  which is fine, I’m the guide now, love too see it! father in law got a 7.5 pounder and a 7, bray got a 5 and a 4.5 all by himself. I managed a dink and lost a couple lol.
Nice catch and good weather to boot.
Nice. There has been a hatch going on. I watched a feeding frenzy happen on Thursday. Heading out in a few minutes to try some bugs.
Nada,water dirtied up for bugs. Maybe the cold snap coming will make some hard water.
